      <span class="section-label">What We Scan</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">The Three Pillars of Email Security</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">These DNS records work together to protect your domain from email spoofing and phishing attacks.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-3">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-content">
          <div style="width: 60px; height: 60px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(227,24,55,0.1); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
